{
  "stem": "26465.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And-- or a woman that has no-- courage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I came to-- to the place, to-- back to my place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that, of course, that way, little by little, things were changing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we came, finally, to the front-- to moment where I was chosen for-- to go to Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why I was chosen, you would ask?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because there were some people, somewhere, somebody, hid Chaya-- I mentioned Chaya-- hid Chaya somewhere, and they wanted Chaya right away, because they wanted her to go to the ghetto, and she never.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, either you give us Chaya or 10 of you will go to Germany, to the camps.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had-- had no idea about that, but things in a little village like that go very quietly, secretly.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] bailiff just chose certain people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And since my brother and I, we were indispensible-- we were dispensable, rather-- we were not necessary.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were chosen probably for other people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, of course, the domestic of Chaya had to send her own daughter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] we were taken to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the train.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a part cattle train, part regular train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "However, the regular train was so destroyed-- practically no windows, and then-- and everything is-- well, it's just probably some-- was in some accident, or something.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And anyway, it doesn't matter, but we were driven there from-- we were taken to school first, exactly at that place where I was reciting the poems.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're taken from that school, and driven to the-- to the-- to the station and packed solid-- body to body-- in those cars-- boxcars and taken to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had no idea, had never ridden a train-- was never on the train before.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the only thing--",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
